Text:
Is she a hot cutie, or a cute hottie? ;-)
Thanks for the upload, Marcco!

Bookworm1960 I'd say a little from column A and a Little from column B. Actually though I am not a big fan of blondes, but that is a personal taste issue, not an issue with the quality of Marcco's posts. Keep up the good work though Marcco, I love most of your stuff. BTW you may need to find a different preview hosting site, seems like myimg.de keeps deleting a lot of your images (not this one, but a lot of others).
